# Base URL for em-solar-api (no trailing slash). Baked in at `vite build` time only.
#
# Local development: run backend with `npm run dev` in em-solar-backend, then:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8787
#
# Live frontend (Cloudflare Pages, Vercel, etc.): set the same variable name in that project’s
# **Build environment variables** — NOT on the API Worker. The API Worker ignores VITE_* keys.
# Production fallback if unset: see DEFAULT_PRODUCTION_API_URL in src/config/api.ts
#
# Optional local test against deployed Worker:
# VITE_API_URL=https://em-solar-backend.ghaffaryasir28.workers.dev
